events.location: Washington, District of Columbia, United States Of America
events.description: All AgesA native of Purcell, Oklahoma, Parker Millsap has released four albums to date and has quickly made a name for himself with his captivating live performances, soulful sound, and character-driven narratives. Hes had a string of highlights in recent years including his network television debut on CONAN, a performance with Elton John at the Apple Music Festival in London, an Austin City Limits taping, and an Americana Music Association nomination for Album of the Year. He has also received praise from The New York Times, Boston Globe, LA Times, Austin Chronicle, and Rolling Stone to name a few.Website / facebook / instagram / spotify / youtube Nat Myers is a Kentucky roots and blues musician, performing original and standards from now to the early 20th century.Website / facebook / instagram / spotify / youtube
